Dr. Kiran exceeded my expectations during my wisdom teeth extraction. The care and comfort provided were exceptional, and I experienced no pain throughout the procedure. Dr. Kiran's reassuring demeanor instills trust, making the entire process smoother. I highly recommend this doctor for anyone in need of dental care—truly a professional with a patient-centered approach.

** *** *** **** ******* * **** *********  ** *** *****.
He is very professional, supportive when explaining the process. Also does not recommend any high level medication or reports at the first analysis itself. Instead his positive approach and right treatment has sorted out issue at the beginning stage.
Treatment place also looks so warm, hygienic and Comfortable.
My family have been pleased with your service and strongly recommend Dr.Kiran for any dental issues.
I’m happy that I’m at the right hands for oral health.
Thank you doctor !!
The care and sincere efforts to ensure waiting time is very very less is unique and the Doctors and their team needs our heartfelt appreciation

My experience has been really good. Both doctor Kiran and Anupama are very good at their work. People unnecessarily feared me of root canal treatment but I  didn’t feel any kind of pain during the treatment . I highly recommend both these doctors for any dental issues.

The doctor has a very calm and composed approch. He explained the problem really.well.and provided multiple options on treatment. There were cheaper to expensive soulutions but he did not push for anything specific. He wanted me to choose based on my budget. I highly recommend him.

The overall experience was Excellent!
Dr. Kiran is really efficient with his Professional Skills. He extracted two wisdom teeth of same side within 30 mins. Thank you for making my dental experience as painless as possible.  Also thanks to Dr.Anupama for motivating me for my further dental concerns.

I would highly recommend Tooth lounge.
